OL,3,CTies, absent winners and anti-war
OL,4,Cslogans: Six key takeaways from the
OL,5,COscars
OL,7,FIt was a big night for the actors and
OL,8,Fdirectors of One Battle After Another
OL,9,Fafter the film swept the Oscars, but
OL,10,Fthe annual Academy Awards show had its
OL,11,Ffair share of memorable moments.
OL,13,FOne Battle After Another won six
OL,14,FOscars on Sunday, including best film,
OL,15,Fwith Sinners being the other big
OL,16,Fwinner of the night.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773662584
OL,3,CTies, absent winners and anti-war
OL,4,Cslogans: Six key takeaways from the
OL,5,COscars
OL,7,FBut the smaller moments of the show
OL,8,Falso shone through, with plenty of
OL,9,Fpolitical speeches, protests against
OL,10,Fthe Iran war and the occasional joke
OL,11,Fat someone else's expense.
OL,13,FHere we take a look at some of the
OL,14,Fmost notable moments of 2026's Academy
OL,15,FAwards.
OL,17,FPaul Thomas Anderson wins best
OL,18,Fdirector after decorated career left
OL,19,Fhim without one
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
