OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773662584
OL,3,CTies, absent winners and anti-war
OL,4,Cslogans: Six key takeaways from the
OL,5,COscars
OL,7,FPaul Thomas Anderson finally won the
OL,8,FOscar for best director on Sunday
OL,9,Fafter decades of critical acclaim but
OL,10,Fno victory in the category.
OL,12,FThe filmmaker, who broke through with
OL,13,FBoogie Nights in 1997, had previously
OL,14,Fbeen nominated for There Will Be Blood
OL,15,Fin 2007, for which Daniel Day-Lewis
OL,16,Fwon best actor, but Anderson failed to
OL,17,Fget the top nod.
OL,19,FThis year, his black comedy action
OL,20,Fthriller One Battle After Another
OL,21,Fsecured him the prize.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
