OL,3,CTies, absent winners and anti-war
OL,4,Cslogans: Six key takeaways from the
OL,5,COscars
OL,7,F"You make a guy work hard for this,"
OL,8,Fhe said while accepting the prize.
OL,10,F"I wrote this movie for my kids, to
OL,11,Fsay sorry for the housekeeping mess
OL,12,Fthat we left in this world we're
OL,13,Fhanding off to them," Anderson said
OL,14,Fonstage after winning for his
OL,15,Fscreenplay.
OL,17,F"But also with the encouragement that
OL,18,Fthey will be the generation that
OL,19,Fhopefully brings us some common sense
OL,20,Fand decency."
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@dO]rD@AOUuD@UO]yD@AOU|D@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/17
