OL,3,CTies, absent winners and anti-war
OL,4,Cslogans: Six key takeaways from the
OL,5,COscars
OL,7,FJessie Buckley and Autumn Durald
OL,8,FArkapaw set records with their wins
OL,10,FSeveral women made history with their
OL,11,Fwins during the ceremony.
OL,13,FJessie Buckley became the first Irish
OL,14,Factor to win best female lead for her
OL,15,Frole in Hamnet and Autumn Durald
OL,16,FArkapaw became the first woman and
OL,17,Fblack person to win the cinematography
OL,18,Faward for Sinners.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
