OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773662584
OL,3,CTies, absent winners and anti-war
OL,4,Cslogans: Six key takeaways from the
OL,5,COscars
OL,7,FThe room erupted when Arkapaw's win
OL,8,Fwas announced, and there was an
OL,9,Felectric energy when she asked all the
OL,10,Fwomen in the Dolby Theatre to stand up
OL,11,Fbecause moments like this don't happen
OL,12,Fwithout women "standing up for you and
OL,13,Fadvocating for you".
OL,15,FActors take stand against war in Iran
OL,16,Fand Gaza
OL,18,FPolitics took central stage for many
OL,19,Fof the artists who attended Sunday's
OL,20,Fshow.
OL,26,@uD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/17
