OL,3,CTies, absent winners and anti-war
OL,4,Cslogans: Six key takeaways from the
OL,5,COscars
OL,7,F"No to war and free Palestine," actor
OL,8,FJavier Bardem said onstage before
OL,9,Fpresenting best international feature
OL,10,Ffilm.
OL,12,FHe wore a patch reading "No a la
OL,13,FGuerra," the same anti-war slogan he
OL,14,Fsported to protest the Iraq war more
OL,15,Fthan two decades ago.
OL,17,FMany actors also criticised the
OL,18,Fdirection of the United States during
OL,19,Fthe ceremony.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
