OL,3,CTies, absent winners and anti-war
OL,4,Cslogans: Six key takeaways from the
OL,5,COscars
OL,7,FHost Conan O'Brien cracked jokes at
OL,8,Fthe expense of the US health care
OL,9,Fsystem and right-wing organisations.
OL,11,FIn a rare moment of sincerity, O'Brien
OL,12,Fsaid the Oscars are particularly
OL,13,Fresonant in "moments like these,"
OL,14,Fnodding broadly at the many different
OL,15,Fworld crises.
OL,17,F"We pay tribute tonight not just to
OL,18,Ffilm, but to the ideals of global
OL,19,Fartistry, collaboration, patience,
OL,20,Fresilience and that rarest of
OL,21,Fqualities today: optimism," he said.
OL,26,@uD@MOUuD@aO]yD@AOU}D@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/17
