OL,3,CTies, absent winners and anti-war
OL,4,Cslogans: Six key takeaways from the
OL,5,COscars
OL,7,FDramatic moment as tied award given in
OL,8,Fbest live action short
OL,10,FSunday saw something truly unusual
OL,11,Fhappen for the Academy Awards: a tie.
OL,13,FThere were two winners for the live
OL,14,Faction short category, which was won
OL,15,Fby both Two People Exchanging Saliva
OL,16,Fand The Singers.
OL,18,FTies are not unprecedented at the
OL,19,FAcademy Awards ` the last occurred in
OL,20,F2013 ` but they remain rare.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773662584
OL,3,CTies, absent winners and anti-war
OL,4,Cslogans: Six key takeaways from the
OL,5,COscars
OL,7,FWhile presenting the award, Kumail
OL,8,FNanjiani said: "It's a tie, I'm not
OL,9,Fjoking, it's actually a tie," before
OL,10,Fadding: "Everyone calm down, we're
OL,11,Fgonna get through this. Focus up, calm
OL,12,Fdown, remain calm."
OL,14,FThe producers were equally surprised,
OL,15,Fwith the duo behind The Singers, Sam
OL,16,FA. Davis and Jack Piatt, saying: "We
OL,17,Fdon't know that was a thing, but we're
OL,18,Fhappy to be up here."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
