OL,3,CTies, absent winners and anti-war
OL,4,Cslogans: Six key takeaways from the
OL,5,COscars
OL,7,FAfter the winners left the stage, host
OL,8,FConan O'Brien congratulated them and
OL,9,Fsaid: "You just ruined 22 million
OL,10,FOscar pools."
OL,12,FSean Penn wins best supporting actor
OL,13,Fwhile absent
OL,15,FAlthough not the top award of the
OL,16,Fnight, Best Supporting Actor is still
OL,17,Fcoveted by many.
OL,26,@qD@GOUrD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/17
