OL,3,CTies, absent winners and anti-war
OL,4,Cslogans: Six key takeaways from the
OL,5,COscars
OL,7,FBut when Sean Penn won the award on
OL,8,FSunday for his role in One Battle
OL,9,FAfter Another, he wasn't there to
OL,10,Faccept it.
OL,12,FLast year's winner, Kieran Culkin,
OL,13,Faccepted the award for him, saying on
OL,14,Fstage: "He couldn't be here tonight,
OL,15,For he didn't want to."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
