OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773662584
OL,3,CTies, absent winners and anti-war
OL,4,Cslogans: Six key takeaways from the
OL,5,COscars
OL,7,FIt's not the first time Penn has been
OL,8,Fan Oscars no-show. He's previously
OL,9,Fskipped the show three times when he
OL,10,Fwas nominated for "Dead Man Walking"
OL,11,Fin 1996, "Sweet and Lowdown" in 2000
OL,12,Fand "I Am Sam" in 2002.
OL,14,FIn 2022, Penn gave one of the Oscar
OL,15,Fstatuettes to Ukrainian President
OL,16,FVolodymyr Zelenskyy.
OL,18,FThere was no explanation given for his
OL,19,Fabsence, but the New York Times
OL,20,Freported he was in Europe and was
OL,21,Fplanning to visit Ukraine.
OL,26,@rD@SOUrD@dO]sD@JOUsD@\O]tD@EOUtD@NO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/17
