OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773662584
OL,3,CTies, absent winners and anti-war
OL,4,Cslogans: Six key takeaways from the
OL,5,COscars
OL,7,FBut she lost out to the team behind
OL,8,FGolden, which appeared in K-Pop Demon
OL,9,FHunters.
OL,11,FWarren was first nominated in 1987,
OL,12,Fand has been nominated on average once
OL,13,Fevery two years.
OL,15,FSpeaking before the ceremony, she
OL,16,Fsaid: "You know, I still haven't won
OL,17,Fthe competitive one. And I'm a
OL,18,Fcompetitive person. It's amazing to
OL,19,Fhave the honorary Oscar - that's
OL,20,Fharder to get than the competitive.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
