OL,3,CTies, absent winners and anti-war
OL,4,Cslogans: Six key takeaways from the
OL,5,COscars
OL,7,F"I don't take that for granted. But,
OL,8,Fyeah, I still want to win.
OL,10,F"My honorary Oscar gets really lonely.
OL,11,FHe wants a friend. He hangs out with
OL,12,FRabbit, my cat, but he prefers to have
OL,13,Fan Oscar buddy."
